note over browser:
user opens single page notes app in browser
end note
browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes

note over browser:
browser sends only one request to the server
end note

note right of server:
 The POST request to the addresss new_note contains the new note as a JSON_data
end note
note left of browser:
Browserstays on the same page and it does not send any further requests.
end note 
note over server:
fetch the form-element from the page, and to register an event handler
end note
server-->browser: HTML-code
note over browser:
event handler creates a new note,adds it to the notes list.
end note
